Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留給這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時光流逝如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}帶走人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你刻下的道道軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:47.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也漸漸染上鏽斑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:49.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}儘管如此
