Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:01.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:08.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:09.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:10.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要再次踏上與你走過的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:16.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕你已經不在那裡
